name: gccsa_g13c_lang_spoken_at_home_by_profic_by_sex_census_2016
title: GCCSA-G13c Language Spoken at Home by Proficiency in Spoken Eng by Sex-Census 2016

legal.licenceType: Creative Commons Attribution 2.5 Australia (CC BY 2.5 AU)

keyword: census,2016,gcp,general community profile,g13c,language,sex,language spoken at home,gccsa,english proficiency
abstract:
GCCSA based data for Language Spoken at Home by Proficiency in Spoken English by Sex, in General Community Profile (GCP), 2016 Census. Count of persons. The list of languages consists of the most common Language Spoken at Home responses reported in the 2011 Census. G13 is broken up into 4 sections (G13a - G13d), this section contains 'Females Speaks Korean Not stated' - 'Persons Speaks German Total'. The data is by GCCSA 2016 boundaries. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
Note: There are small random adjustments made to all cell values to protect the confidentiality of data. These adjustments may cause the sum of rows or columns to differ by small amounts from table totals.
For more information visit the data source: http://www.abs.gov.au/census.
